{"tid":639224,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[完了吧] 係A必贏呀","createTime":"2018-04-23T10:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T12:36:26.000Z","uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"c2337fbc9b2044aa4ef890180ad97035395eff2c","tid":639224,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T10:11:05.000Z","msg":"今日一開連登, 睇到成版 又a 又b,<br />\n<br />\n為咗唔需要再眼冤, 我決定Kill咗呢個討論去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/181020_b44da42edae7423cf10d37cb085054ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F181020_b44da42edae7423cf10d37cb085054ab.png&h=b858b38f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nA: 34455QQKKA2<br />\nB: 622<br />\n<br />\n<em>(*以下粗體一方代表下一回合出牌先)</em><br />\n<br />\nA要贏, 即係 出現以下情況<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">情況一</span><br />\n<strong>A: 任何一隻牌, 2</strong> <br />\nB: 任何牌<br />\n<br />\n或者<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">情況二</span><br />\n<strong>A: 任何一Pair</strong> <br />\nB: 任何牌<br />\n<br />\nB要贏, 即係 出現以下情況:<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">情況三</span><br />\nA: (任何牌)<br />\n<strong>B: <span style=\"color: red;\"><del>22</del></span> 6</strong> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">情況四</span> 上手出雙<br />\nA: (任何牌)<br />\n<strong>B: <span style=\"color: red;\"><del>6</del></span> 22</strong> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">情況五</span> 上手出單隻<br />\nA: (任何三隻單丁牌)<br />\n<strong>B: <span style=\"color: red;\"><del>6</del></span> 22</strong> <br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講, <br />\n如果雙方都知對方嘅牌, 必然會打到呢一步: (下一手A出牌)<br />\n<strong>A: KKA2</strong><br />\nB: <span style=\"color: red;\"><del>6</del></span> 22<br />\n<br />\nA 呢一手只要出A, <br />\n之後必然出現<span style=\"color: blue;\">情況一</span> 或 <span style=\"color: blue;\">情況二</span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>完。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b182f559d0b1c4926e4b72545416dd795bd05994","tid":639224,"uid":5